yingyinNormal.zh: 你还记得么，几个月以前，我告诉过你引擎检修灯在闪。

yingyinNormal.en: We are Zhaoqing eighth station which one of several stops inland from Zhaoqing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们在肇庆第8站，是从肇庆出来的几个站点之一。

yingyinNormal.en: Which hosts? I don't know, several of them. It had to have been the older models.
yingyinNormal.zh: 哪些接待员？我不知道，有好几个，肯定得是那些老款的机器才行。

yingyinNormal.en: It's scarlet fever. He'll be in bed for several months, at least. Complete isolation.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是猩红热。他至少需要卧床几个月。完全隔离。

yingyinNormal.en: Initially, she had some success battling her illness, but it's come back full force the last several months.
yingyinNormal.zh: 起初，她在与病魔的抗争中取得了胜利，但这几个月，疾病复发而且非常严重。

yingyinNormal.en: Loss is a sobering phenomenon. Several months ago, I almost lost my husband. Our nation almost lost a President.
yingyinNormal.zh: 失去让我们深思，几个月前，我差点失去了我的丈夫，我们的国家差点失去了总统。

yingyinNormal.en: He didn't arrive until several hours later, which means he couldn't have seen his wife's killer leaving the scene. He lied.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他是几个小时后才到家的，就是说，他不可能看到杀害他妻子的凶手离开现场，他撒谎了。

yingyinNormal.en: I mean, you can't know this, but in several of them. People viewed your little trick with the berries as an act of defiance, not as an act of love.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不过这一点你并不知情，事实上有几个区的人把你的毒浆果小把戏看作是挑衅，而并不是爱情使然。

yingyinNormal.en: Amanda's needling takes several hours, half a day at least.
yingyinNormal.zh: 阿曼达的针术需要几小时至少半天才能见效。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, I had sex with him in the back of a limo. Several times.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我和他还在轿车后座里发生关系。好几次呢。

yingyinNormal.en: See there are still several areas that haven't been fully excavated.
yingyinNormal.zh: 因为里面还有些地区还没完全开挖的。

yingyinNormal.en: For the last several years, you've been a familiar face. Must get exhausting.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这几年来，你一直左右逢源。一定很累人。

yingyinNormal.en: I've invited you all here for several reasons, but first, I have an announcement.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我邀请你们来的原因有很多，不过首先我要宣布一件事情。

yingyinNormal.en: Professor, my cells are reproducing at a phenomenal speed. Several million per second.
yingyinNormal.zh: 教授，我的细胞正在飞速增长，每秒增生几百万个。

yingyinNormal.en: It's a simple matter. There are several toxic chemicals that'd be untraceable in an autopsy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这其实很简单，有那么几种有毒化学物尸检是查不出来的。

yingyinNormal.en: Ski Dubai is even home to troupe of snow penguins, which come out to play several times each day.
yingyinNormal.zh: 室内滑雪场内还有企鹅剧团，每日演出数次。

yingyinNormal.en: Harold? What happened? I was running several iterations of the A.I. to see which one worked best.
yingyinNormal.zh: 哈罗德？怎么回事？我运行了人工智能的多个迭代，想看哪个性能最佳。

yingyinNormal.en: Several million years ago, a gene plague caused by cloning nearly annihilated the entire human race.
yingyinNormal.zh: 几百万年前尤克隆导致的基因灾祸几乎使整个人类都灭绝了。

yingyinNormal.en: Isn't that the girl that told the entire school and, oh, several colleges, that you had a drug problem?
yingyinNormal.zh: 她不就是那个告诉全校，哦，是几间大学 ，说你在磕药？

yingyinNormal.en: Take this guy. I mean, look, no offense, but you look like you've been taken to the cleaners several times.
yingyinNormal.zh: 比如说，这个，无意冒犯，不过你看着像赔过不少钱。

sense_info_list.en: consisting of more than two but not very many

examination_example.sentence: At the same time, the European Union, Spain, Britain and <highlight>several</highlight> other countries have all seriously contemplated digital services taxes.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 与此同时，欧盟、西班牙、英国和其他几个国家都在认真考虑征收数字服务税。

examination_example.sentence: American farmers have been complaining of labor shortages for <highlight>several</highlight> years.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 几年来，美国农民一直在抱怨劳动力短缺。

examination_example.sentence: Yet, in <highlight>several</highlight> instances, justices acted in ways that weakened the court's reputation for being independent and impartial.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 然而，在一些情况下，法官的行为方式削弱了法院独立、公正的名声。
